OL,3,CRapist threatened to throw woman off
OL,4,CTunisia hotel balcony
OL,6,FA man who suffocated a woman before
OL,7,Furinating on her and threatening to
OL,8,Fthrow her from a hotel balcony while
OL,9,Fon holiday has been jailed for 21
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FAlex Owers' victim lost consciousness
OL,13,Fduring the attack in a hotel room in
OL,14,FTunisia in January 2025.
OL,16,FHe was arrested on his return to the
OL,17,FUK, when the woman disclosed that he
OL,18,Fhad repeatedly attacked and raped her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
