OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782301688
OL,3,CRapist threatened to throw woman off
OL,4,CTunisia hotel balcony
OL,6,FOwers, 46, was convicted of one count
OL,7,Fof intentional strangulation, two of
OL,8,Fsuffocation, and two of assault
OL,9,Fcausing actual bodily harm following a
OL,10,Ftrial in August 2025.
OL,12,FHe was also found guilty of five
OL,13,Fcounts of rape following a retrial at
OL,14,FGrimsby Crown Court in April of this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FSpeaking as Owers was jailed, the
OL,18,Fwoman said: "Even though you're
OL,19,Fimprisoned, I barricade all my doors
OL,20,Fout of fear that you have escaped and
OL,21,Fwill come to kill me."
OL,26,@zD@MOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
