PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782301688
OL,3,CRapist threatened to throw woman off
OL,4,CTunisia hotel balcony
OL,6,FHumberside Police said Owers put a
OL,7,Fpillow over his victim's face and
OL,8,Fstrangled her until she blacked out in
OL,9,Fthe attack on 3 January 2025.
OL,11,FHe then dragged her back into the room
OL,12,Fwhen she tried to escape and punched
OL,13,Fher in the ribs.
OL,15,FPolice said Owers urinated on the
OL,16,Fwoman and threatened to throw her from
OL,17,Fthe balcony "in an attempt to make her
OL,18,Fdeath look non accidental".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
