PN,33904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782301688
OL,3,CRapist threatened to throw woman off
OL,4,CTunisia hotel balcony
OL,6,FAn investigation was launched after
OL,7,Fofficers received a report from a
OL,8,Fthird party.
OL,10,FOwers was arrested by Essex Police
OL,11,Fwhen he arrived at Stansted Airport.
OL,13,FAs well as his prison sentence, he was
OL,14,Fgiven a lifelong restraining order and
OL,15,Fwill be on the Sex Offenders Register
OL,16,Ffor life.
OL,18,FIn a statement, the victim told Owers
OL,19,Fshe almost died at his hands.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
