PN,33905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782301688
OL,3,CRapist threatened to throw woman off
OL,4,CTunisia hotel balcony
OL,6,F"I still feel your hands around my
OL,7,Fthroat and the pillow over my face,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"You held me against my will and put
OL,11,Fme through three hours of pure hell
OL,12,Fand suffering.
OL,14,F"That night haunts me to this very day
OL,15,Fand will forever. I live in constant
OL,16,Fpanic and fear and jump at the
OL,17,Fslightest noise thinking it's you
OL,18,Fcoming to finish what you started on
OL,19,Fthat horrific night."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
