CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1782301688
OL,3,CRapist threatened to throw woman off
OL,4,CTunisia hotel balcony
OL,6,FDet Con Sam Atkinson said: "These
OL,7,Foffences were appalling and deeply
OL,8,Fviolating. The level of abuse and
OL,9,Fviolence Owers subjected a woman to
OL,10,Fshowed complete disregard for her
OL,11,Fwellbeing, dignity and safety.
OL,13,F"I would like to commend the bravery
OL,14,Fof the woman coming forward and
OL,15,Fthroughout all the court proceedings."
OL,26,@nD@\OUuD@AOU
